Ramada Inc is raising 100 mln dlrsthrough an offering of subordinated notes due 1999 yielding11.703 pct, said sole manager Salomon Brothers Inc.    The notes have an 11-5/8 pct coupon and were priced at99.50, Salomon said.    Non-callable for three years and non-refundable for five,the issue is rated B-2 by Moody's Investors Service Inc andB-minus by Standard and Poor's Corp. Reuter&#3;